{"tid":1097584,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Can we train our own AI robot to vote for us?","createTime":"2019-04-08T12:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T02:34:37.000Z","uid":46488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0f628fa247384f923cd468a98d125684f194c18c","tid":1097584,"uid":46488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:54:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CyGWML6cI_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCyGWML6cI_k&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfpyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=6e012052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CyGWML6cI_k</a>"},{"pid":"7f27275a910b7bcb41850f380de9378a17abfc9b","tid":1097584,"uid":46488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"大致上:<br />\n點解我哋需要用議會代表制, 係因為我哋無法喺日常生活中撥冗睇咁多條議案<br />\n所以我哋可以train一個robot, 令到佢可以根據我哋以往既思維同對新方案既資料自行投票<br />\n咁我哋只需要考慮十份一既議案就可以有一個比現有&quot;議員&quot;更好既&quot;代表"},{"pid":"550f4ec61bd72bb4299d9f1026ee6b99428d589d","tid":1097584,"uid":46488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:17:04.000Z","msg":"諗咗諗, 呢個諗法大體上都係比現有方案更好既pareto improvement<br />\n至少喺香港實行既話, 你就唔洗含淚投泛民<br />\n<br />\n但條片有樣嘢肯定唔啱, 就係algorithm因為open-source就可以無cheating<br />\n因為寫AI algorithm係一件好難既事<br />\n尤其呢啲咁複雜, 唔係single objective oriented既AI<br />\n以現有科技我覺得係做到呢啲AI, 但只有big tech先會做到, 由一個individual engineering做出嚟既根本唔實際<br />\n最尾就會變咗google/MS/apple/Amazon dominate, tech company就會有好大political power"},{"pid":"05559b14a0a9bb378ae2d8499c8d62d06faa6c46","tid":1097584,"uid":170252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"550f4ec61bd72bb4299d9f1026ee6b99428d589d","tid":1097584,"uid":46488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:17:04.000Z","msg":"諗咗諗, 呢個諗法大體上都係比現有方案更好既pareto improvement<br />\n至少喺香港實行既話, 你就唔洗含淚投泛民<br />\n<br />\n但條片有樣嘢肯定唔啱, 就係algorithm因為open-source就可以無cheating<br />\n因為寫AI algorithm係一件好難既事<b